MozActivity demo Open Web Apps

* developer: Gergo Istvan Nagy
* email: gergo.istvan.nagy[at]]mozilla[dot]hu

These applications are samples to demonstrate how to create and handle MozActivity in Firefox OS.

Check documentation for further information:
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/WebAPI/Web_Activities#Activity_handler_description
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Apps/Manifest

Deploy:

    volo serve

Build:

    volo build

This will run the "build" command in the volofile that is in this directory.

That build command creates an optimized version of the project in a
**www-built** directory. The js/app.js file will be optimized to include
all of its dependencies.

For more information on the optimizer:
http://requirejs.org/docs/optimization.html

For more information on using requirejs:
http://requirejs.org/docs/api.html
